{"tid":292304,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人男朋友都係咁","createTime":"2017-06-21T09:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T06:54:33.000Z","uid":15015,"like":1,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b6aebf87d2e567e97ab05561766460117dd4e27","tid":292304,"uid":15015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:22:44.000Z","msg":"成日都覺得佢睇我唔起<br />\n我今年21 仲讀緊書 佢25 已經有份穩定職業<br />\n講多少少背景 我住公屋 佢住私樓 屋企仲有層樓收緊租<br />\n<br />\n有次同佢啲朋友一齊食飯 講起買樓<br />\n佢一句西埋黎話：「你唔係覺得你靠自己可以買到樓掛？讀埋啲垃圾u 垃圾科 出嚟咪又係打份閪工 到時畢業搵份文職輕輕鬆鬆等我養算啦」<br />\n我諗成件事換個方法講會好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢係都要講得咁鬼難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又成日有意無意串我住公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實佢平時對我好好 但有啲時候真係覺得佢好唔尊重我 咁睇我唔起當初做咩要追我啫屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為依樣野已經嘈過好多次 又試過分手 次次都心軟比佢氹返 到底係咪自己犯賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552b0930878dac7e13b0c5904c8209de7c15b2d7","tid":292304,"uid":21423,"like":12,"dislike":7,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:25:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9189acb11e897e21d29c2d9a00b172b1f7716cb","tid":292304,"uid":96979,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:26:09.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個感覺真係唔好受既"},{"pid":"27bcb742084a10804970c0c8cf4dc7577ca4fb4c","tid":292304,"uid":59231,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:26:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢都話養你啦，你仲想點呀，死港零</blockquote><br />\n識波呀ching"},{"pid":"70aa311071980aea6ca5dfe5b478dfc0e8408256","tid":292304,"uid":10141,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:26:42.000Z","msg":"呢啲男人嘅態度好難頂，一定係平時周圍認屎認屁嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322d32756b04008eae200d2ac1f5a1fecea47863","tid":292304,"uid":20302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:27:15.000Z","msg":"遲早散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57707a1d552f18ec5058cc34da941d9b1eca380f","tid":292304,"uid":7567,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:29:51.000Z","msg":"你咪又係貪人有樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff60f0741cf4caca5ad572719be6adea9a93781b","tid":292304,"uid":2506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:31:17.000Z","msg":"我無睇唔起我女朋友 但我一直覺得公屋係鬼地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我女朋友住公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c45ce403cae0f755fcabf5b2ea63696a0010a6","tid":292304,"uid":649,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:32:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲男人嘅態度好難頂，一定係平時周圍認屎認屁嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n靠老豆老母仲咁口響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a286d55d1e43094e835cc75ad59f09fe6265876","tid":292304,"uid":15015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:34:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲男人嘅態度好難頂，一定係平時周圍認屎認屁嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一時時啦 又唔見佢對其他人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 脾氣好撚差就真嘅 成日要硬食佢啲脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4552e775f0a6c016c0377991debdac3cb30af3","tid":292304,"uid":43466,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日都覺得佢睇我唔起<br />\n我今年21 仲讀緊書 佢25 已經有份穩定職業<br />\n講多少少背景 我住公屋 佢住私樓 屋企仲有層樓收緊租<br />\n<br />\n有次同佢啲朋友一齊食飯 講起買樓<br />\n佢一句西埋黎話：「你唔係覺得你靠自己可以買到樓掛？讀埋啲垃圾u 垃圾科 出嚟咪又係打份閪工 到時畢業搵份文職輕輕鬆鬆等我養算啦」<br />\n我諗成件事換個方法講會好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢係都要講得咁鬼難聽<img src=